Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.30,0:01:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(所羅門攻略戰)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.86,0:02:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三艦隊，從後方接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.59,0:02:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色基地聽到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.90,0:02:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到了，請說！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.17,0:02:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後準備補給
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.97,0:02:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,改變航路\N進入同樣的隊形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.87,0:02:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進入補給狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.94,0:02:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告訴他明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.61,0:02:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輸送艦波倫布司\N向右前方駛去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.65,0:02:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快準備補給
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.65,0:02:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去和司令打招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.79,0:02:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼我不可以去？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.62,0:02:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要和司令打招呼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.92,0:02:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又不是去玩\N有什麼好去的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.13,0:02:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯了，只是去打招呼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.33,0:02:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史中尉\N不如幫一幫忙，好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.13,0:02:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣死人了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.25,0:03:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿著火箭的\N那怪傢伙是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.62,0:03:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是突襲快艇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.59,0:03:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突襲快艇？\N又不是要去打仗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.76,0:03:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提起也怕怕！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.10,0:03:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎，待會再見！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.57,0:03:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長，白色基地艦長\N來了等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.87,0:03:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.14,0:03:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是布萊特中尉，請指教！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.84,0:03:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你了，布萊特！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.94,0:03:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很久不見了，馬健司令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.58,0:03:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要叫我做司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.58,0:03:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些大人物一到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.25,0:03:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就成為小人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.35,0:03:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你現在很有指揮官的氣勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.83,0:03:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不錯呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.46,0:04:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過來看看！         是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.46,0:04:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們現在\N行駛中的路線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.47,0:04:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會將所有軍力\N集中過來的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.17,0:04:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說\N目的地是所羅門嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.97,0:04:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，白色基地和我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.81,0:04:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是去攻擊所羅門的\N先鋒部隊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.21,0:04:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎！任務相當艱巨呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.55,0:04:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們可以做得到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.98,0:04:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能夠提出\N這個問題和我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.19,0:04:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,足以證明你是有能力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.76,0:04:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定不會有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，母艦上的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.66,0:04:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經超時工作了！\N特別是阿姆羅...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.80,0:04:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀！你指那個\N駕駛鋼彈的少年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.63,0:04:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他算是個天才\N和我們不同的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.00,0:04:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不同的嗎？\N你說不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.18,0:04:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼電壓\N會裝不上去的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.44,0:04:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那便糟了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.91,0:04:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃飯了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.79,0:05:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼不妥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.45,0:05:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...只要放下便可以了\N多謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.46,0:05:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能我太倦了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.91,0:05:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們只送一個畢克．薩姆的\N機動堡壘來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.91,0:05:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！只是得一個！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.08,0:05:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底多姆在做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.15,0:05:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠這些多姆的數量\N怎會夠...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.55,0:05:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若只得一個新型機的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.12,0:05:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒不如給我\N十台多姆還好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.16,0:05:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的...      什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.16,0:05:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個畢克．薩姆還是在試作階段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.30,0:05:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然已在急速進行...\N但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.27,0:05:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各方面來的訂單\N實在太多了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.77,0:05:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算數吧！         是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.84,0:05:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快將畢克．薩姆組合好！   是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.77,0:05:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布加，現在還未知\N帝姆艦隊在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.11,0:05:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的對不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.61,0:05:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為現在米諾夫斯基粒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.25,0:06:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,濃度最高的地方作探測\N所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.88,0:06:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要盡快找到他們！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.20,0:06:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立刻除去固定軸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.73,0:06:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開啟輸送管\N開啟所有通道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.94,0:06:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開港外通道\N立刻準備離港！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.85,0:06:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩你了，卡姆蘭檢察官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.65,0:06:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問解除封條了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.12,0:06:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已解除了\N但請別胡亂開火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.66,0:06:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有請你們快離開\N以後別再來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.90,0:06:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望你說話客氣一些\N卡姆蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.90,0:06:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.97,0:06:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星六號能夠\N平安茍存到今日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.50,0:06:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是吉翁軍手下留情！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.77,0:07:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是否還要我多謝你們嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.51,0:07:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拉，妳在做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.98,0:07:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她...她是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.65,0:07:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就當是我的妹妹吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.12,0:08:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在，我們艦隊的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.99,0:08:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由所羅門計起來\N應該是第三戰區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.62,0:08:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是鼻尖的位置！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.63,0:08:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裡，我們已\N再沒任何障礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.99,0:08:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阻礙住去所羅門的路線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.70,0:08:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.23,0:08:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請各艦隊排成橫一字形！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.91,0:08:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙勞‧波，小琪她們怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.81,0:08:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們在五號室\N有重力的那間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.91,0:08:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈囉也在？         是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.15,0:08:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小琪，妳知不知\N為何要穿成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.52,0:08:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為不穿成這樣\N是不可去打仗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.92,0:08:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起初由正面攻擊\N跟著用雷射光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.16,0:08:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後大家由缺口攻入去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.33,0:09:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？你不是說笑吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.20,0:09:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,單就這樣的兵力...\N去攻擊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.16,0:09:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豈不是去自殺嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.50,0:09:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用擔心，凱\N聯邦軍會想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.53,0:09:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎可叫我可放心呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.50,0:09:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說得太多了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.87,0:09:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要相信帝姆艦隊的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.18,0:09:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位只要維持\N5分鐘就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.35,0:09:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到那時，本軍會用\N攻擊要塞武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.45,0:09:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊要塞武器？\N是什麼武器的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.62,0:09:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始攻擊！速度加八度！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.49,0:09:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突襲快艇準備！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.36,0:09:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2...1...0...出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.15,0:09:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底敵軍的\N移動情形怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.48,0:09:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，他們已集合在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.82,0:10:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向我們接近\N可以使用雷射炮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.62,0:10:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！通通擊沉他們！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.40,0:10:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火箭炮，主炮\N雷射炮開始攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.50,0:10:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.13,0:10:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人發射了雷射擾亂網！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.14,0:10:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多姆，各MS\N出擊應付敵人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.17,0:10:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵軍數目不多\N改用火箭可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.48,0:10:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,密特艦隊向左面伸展過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.65,0:11:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,附助機部隊在後方別動！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.28,0:11:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帝姆主力艦\N會由那邊來的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.32,0:11:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷射優亂綱成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.82,0:11:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！各艦隊各自進攻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.33,0:11:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本艦現立即出動！\N吉姆立即出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.10,0:11:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士\NG戰機，出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.44,0:11:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家記著，要共同作戰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.88,0:11:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家別遲到啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.45,0:11:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會努力作戰的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.95,0:11:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，現在出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.82,0:11:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼加農，出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.36,0:11:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.65,0:12:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個就是...戰場？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.18,0:12:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡，看我的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.25,0:12:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一個呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.46,0:12:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱，要小心敵人呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.63,0:12:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，妳真可愛呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.97,0:13:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬加，替我指揮一會！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.84,0:13:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，將軍！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.84,0:13:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很快回來的！      是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.81,0:13:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬全之策\N女仕請全部退避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.15,0:13:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到逃生船去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.85,0:13:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰局對我們不利嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.42,0:13:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點！         是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.56,0:13:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所羅門是不會被攻陷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.83,0:13:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這只是為安全計！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.33,0:13:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所謂不怕一萬，只怕萬一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.60,0:13:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,況且，也是為了\N小寶貝的安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.10,0:13:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太大聲了，嚇壞她呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.58,0:13:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.68,0:13:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，再過一些\N再一些，是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.63,0:14:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生或死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信只有在戰爭後才知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.84,0:14:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過有一點可以肯定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.34,0:14:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當每次閃起美麗的光輝時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.14,0:14:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就會有數個人甚至數百人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.91,0:14:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變成太空一粒小塵而消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.27,0:14:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反射鏡準備得怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.84,0:14:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！大約\N四分鐘左右便行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.27,0:14:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來敵軍快將發現我們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.11,0:14:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？蠢材！現在才發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.81,0:14:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵軍躲在岩石後面？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.91,0:14:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.11,0:14:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是帝姆！敵軍的主力艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.81,0:14:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不快攻擊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.59,0:15:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.83,0:15:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派武斷號和天力號\N去封付敵主力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.63,0:15:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要第七團派援軍來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.17,0:15:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希莉亞？\N豈非會給國民成笑話？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.88,0:15:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反射鏡裝置妥當！\N在主力軸上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.32,0:15:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,電能已經連接好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.59,0:15:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反射戰術開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.22,0:15:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目標是所羅門右翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.82,0:15:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙大門！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.27,0:15:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反射開始倒數十秒！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.01,0:15:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有敵艦接近，小心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.91,0:15:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必理它，快對準重點！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.28,0:16:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三...二...焦點...對準！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.64,0:16:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所羅門...燒著了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.74,0:16:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯邦軍的\N新武器威力很利害！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.51,0:16:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.75,0:16:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的宇宙大門破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.92,0:16:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是敵軍的新武器！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.19,0:16:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.75,0:16:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷達仍可用\N但發電機就失效了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.99,0:16:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯邦軍攻入來了嗎？\N位置在那裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.99,0:16:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵軍主力艦隊來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.89,0:16:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主力艦應該\N可以應付到的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.96,0:16:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,報告\N有數百小飛彈來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.30,0:16:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要向那邊攻擊才是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.14,0:17:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.01,0:17:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了...\N連槍彈口也沒有了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.15,0:17:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是先回去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.96,0:17:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色基地已歸航\N損傷程度B
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.69,0:17:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人負傷，因為坦克撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.73,0:17:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以戰鬥力下降了11%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.86,0:17:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人和很多人也受了傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.73,0:17:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如由我\N到醫療室幫忙吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.94,0:17:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，保羅\N你代替芙勞‧波的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.07,0:17:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，我來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.48,0:17:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正木上仕\N請妳準備輸血吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.49,0:17:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很快會康復的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.46,0:17:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事我可以幫忙的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.09,0:17:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫我拿AB型血槳\N及輸血設備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.10,0:17:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人？         快點！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.47,0:18:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵軍主力艦來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.10,0:18:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用衛星火箭攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.10,0:18:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將基地內\N所有導彈發射出去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.35,0:18:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最重要的是\N為隼人多輸一樽血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.18,0:18:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請記住！         是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.65,0:18:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即管來吧！   多姆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.69,0:18:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙勞‧波...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.96,0:18:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你別激動\N已經充份地作戰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.80,0:18:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嗎？所以要安靜啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.20,0:18:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.63,0:18:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們沒事，還在作戰中！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.50,0:18:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.87,0:18:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是沒用！\N還在這樣子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.04,0:18:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連雪拉和凱也及不上...\N可惡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.18,0:18:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎可以這樣說，隼人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.15,0:18:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是已經很英勇嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.49,0:18:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳不用來安慰我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.49,0:18:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不怕老實對妳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.02,0:18:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自從我上了母艦後\N到現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.49,0:19:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直都還想贏阿姆羅的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.66,0:19:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但結果...\N始終無法勝過他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.66,0:19:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人，阿姆羅他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.27,0:19:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是和我們不同的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.50,0:19:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我們不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.45,0:19:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二和第六戰鬥隊\N已沒回音！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.02,0:19:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武斷號亦失去聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.12,0:19:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬加，給我一杯咖啡   是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.79,0:19:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吩咐所有MS出去防守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.03,0:19:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要將敵人全部消滅！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.81,0:19:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們想撤退？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.38,0:19:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從那裡衝入去較好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.48,0:19:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裡，是被新武器\N所毀壞的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.22,0:19:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真利害！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.72,0:20:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.53,0:20:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母艦有電訊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.33,0:20:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說鋼彈已攻入基地內了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.90,0:20:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！吩咐\N各艦隊MS出去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.84,0:20:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！各艦隊\N請聽主艦命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.77,0:20:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派吉姆和鐵球及\N各登陸部隊出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.69,0:20:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望大家\N可以順利攻入去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.28,0:21:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所羅門要求支援？   是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.88,0:21:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由暗碼打來的\N詳情仍未清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.35,0:21:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是希莉亞將軍吩咐的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.89,0:21:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要求我們出戰\N支援所羅門！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.16,0:21:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拉，怎樣？\N我們要進入戰場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.67,0:21:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贊斯巴爾，全速前進！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.97,0:21:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目的地，所羅門！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.84,0:21:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各人回去作戰崗位！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.89,0:21:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還生存嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.70,0:21:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊，加油啊！\N妳要繼續努力啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.00,0:21:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邵娜在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.80,0:21:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,親愛的\N這裡是不安全嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.21,0:22:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別胡說\N所羅門不會淪陷的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.81,0:22:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...         聽我說！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.61,0:22:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想妳去姊姊的\N格拉納達處避避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.81,0:22:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡怎辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.21,0:22:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擔心，這裡沒事的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.65,0:22:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寶貝交給妳了！\N妳要養育她成人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.35,0:22:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嗎？邵娜！      你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.69,0:22:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我是一個軍人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.13,0:22:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以要維護\N我們薩比家軍人的尊嚴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.30,0:22:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.77,0:22:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點，帶同寶寶\N一起走，邵娜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.65,0:22:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,編成MS作戰隊伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.45,0:22:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人快登陸了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.18,0:22:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薩克，多姆準備出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.02,0:22:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武裝火箭炮部隊\N全出戰對付敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.32,0:22:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢克．薩姆準備妥當沒有？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.62,0:22:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在準備要大進攻了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.90,0:23:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個...就是畢克．薩姆！

